1
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,680
Lu Zhen'an, don't rush.

2
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:25,400
The best is yet to come.

3
00:01:26,960 --> 00:01:28,480
We've informed the bank.

4
00:01:28,600 --> 00:01:30,720
They'll withdraw the loan
once the test fails,

5
00:01:30,720 --> 00:01:32,400
and the news headline will be

6
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:35,720
"Genius Engineer Su Minghao
Fakes Data for Investment:

7
00:01:35,720 --> 00:01:37,920
10-Billion-Yuan Project Collapses."

8
00:01:45,600 --> 00:01:46,360
Minghao.

9
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:50,840
You...

10
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:53,600
Minghao.

11
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:56,360
I'm doomed.

12
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:59,479
The factory has been sealed off,

13
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:01,080
the house is mortgaged,

14
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:05,900
and the debt collectors are at my door
threatening to chop off my hand.

15
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:06,920
Minghao,

16
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:09,680
you're my only hope now.

17
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,240
How much is that

18
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,500
battery patent worth?

19
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,280
I'm begging you.

20
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:38,520
Zhen'an,

21
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:43,240
this is everything I've worked for
over the past ten years.

22
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:44,970
But you're the only one I trust.

23
00:02:48,640 --> 00:02:49,320
Take it.

24
00:02:51,079 --> 00:02:52,410
Let's do this together.

25
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,760
We're getting reports

26
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:06,560
that Qiming Tech's new battery
won an international gold award.

27
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,840
It has broken through industry barriers

28
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:09,160
and set a new benchmark for the sector,

29
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:10,280
with a valuation
exceeding one billion yuan.

30
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,320
Change it like this.

31
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:12,800
Look, the battery is broken.

32
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:13,560
Mr. Su,

33
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:16,120
look, we just got our certificate.

34
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,079
Congratulations.

35
00:03:19,079 --> 00:03:20,720
Years of work finally paid off.

36
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:23,180
I bet everything I had
to build this company.

37
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:26,079
Why does he get to

38
00:03:26,079 --> 00:03:29,610
hold 60 percent of the shares
just for his technical expertise?

39
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:32,000
Both the patent

40
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,760
and the company are mine.

41
00:03:33,760 --> 00:03:35,160
No one can take them away!

42
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:45,040
Mr. Lu, at today's opening,

43
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:47,440
our market value exceeded 20 billion yuan.

44
00:03:50,640 --> 00:03:52,240
Has the patent been renamed?

45
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:53,240
Yes.

46
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,480
Today is Su Minghao's funeral.

47
00:03:57,480 --> 00:03:58,520
Prepare for it.

48
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,200
Okay.

49
00:04:06,920 --> 00:04:09,280
To Zhen'an.

50
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,800
I'm entrusting my daughters to you.

51
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,360
Xia is seven,

52
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:18,640
and Dong is 17.

53
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:23,440
Faithfully, Minghao.

54
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:28,880
No one saw this coming.

55
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:31,720
Don't worry.

56
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:35,080
I'll deal with the debts.

57
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,720
From now on, I'll take care of

58
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:40,280
Xia and you.

59
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:42,520
Minghao,

60
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:46,120
you're more useful dead than alive.

61
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:48,480
We were brothers.

62
00:04:51,159 --> 00:04:52,200
Rest in peace.

63
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:55,570
I'll take good care of your daughters.

64
00:04:58,440 --> 00:04:59,280
Dad,

65
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:02,280
you can finally rest in peace.

66
00:05:17,840 --> 00:05:18,680
Su Dong!

67
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:19,760
Su Dong!

68
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:20,960
Su Dong!

69
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:25,160
I only want to know one thing.

70
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:28,120
Have you ever loved me?

71
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:34,120
I've been living in hell all these years.

72
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:36,360
Now, welcome to hell,

73
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,840
dear brother.

74
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:40,080
Lu Zhen'an,

75
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:42,360
do you like the surprise

76
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:43,480
I prepared for you?

77
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:45,960
Su Xia!

78
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,200
Chairman!

79
00:05:50,400 --> 00:05:51,120
Chairman!

80
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:52,200
Chairman!

81
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,080
Dad!

82
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:19,440
Young Master!

83
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:22,280
Young Master, it's all my fault!

84
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:24,720
Young Master, have mercy!

85
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:27,560
Listen,

86
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:28,560
I'm so sorry.

87
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:30,920
I was greedy and lustful.

88
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:33,100
I sold you out to our enemy.

89
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,520
Now that you've beaten me

90
00:06:34,640 --> 00:06:35,900
and vented your anger,

91
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:37,000
please let me go!

92
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:38,120
I've served

93
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:39,960
your family

94
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:43,680
for more than 20 years!

95
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:45,480
Please let me go!

96
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:46,880
Have mercy!

97
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,280
Young Master!

98
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:49,970
Young Master...

99
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:52,060
Have mercy, Young Master!

100
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,120
Young Master!

101
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:57,760
Have mercy?

102
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:02,240
That'd be the greatest insult
to my family.

103
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:07,240
He's yours.

104
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:09,520
Do whatever you want.

105
00:07:10,080 --> 00:07:11,720
Young Master!

106
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:12,960
Young Master!

107
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:23,040
Dad jumped from here.

108
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:26,800
Back then, the rebar was still exposed.

109
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,440
Now it looks like

110
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:31,200
a golden cage.

111
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,720
Just like the Lu family.

112
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:36,720
Sister, help! Sister!

113
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:38,360
Please let my sister go!

114
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:41,240
I... I apologize for her!

115
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:43,720
Tell me,

116
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:45,040
or I'll beat you to death!

117
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,440
Tell me, who is it?

118
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:50,480
Sister, where are you?

119
00:07:51,840 --> 00:07:54,080
When I took you to the Lu residence,

120
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,610
you were only seven.

121
00:07:57,320 --> 00:08:00,050
When you found out
I was going to marry Lu Zhen'an,

122
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:03,160
you stared at me like I was a traitor.

123
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:04,800
I always hoped

124
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:07,860
you'd understand everything

125
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:09,600
when we got our revenge.

126
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,520
Yes, I understand now.

127
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:14,220
I understand why you allowed them

128
00:08:14,280 --> 00:08:15,840
to trample on your dignity.

129
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:19,240
I understand why you tried
to provoke Lu Fan.

130
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,640
And I totally understand

131
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:24,500
the look on your face
when you saw me seducing Lu Fan.

132
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:28,520
Xia.

133
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:30,880
Did we...

134
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:33,440
take the wrong path?

135
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:39,570
We sacrificed your childhood,

136
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:41,640
my innocence,

137
00:08:42,520 --> 00:08:43,880
and Lu Fan's life

138
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:47,120
to make those people suffer.

139
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:52,440
I don't know.

140
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:13,480
This is what was left in Dad's pocket

141
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:16,000
the day he jumped off the building,

142
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,530
the only thing he had on him.

143
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:29,840
Dad, why are you still sleeping?

144
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:31,600
Lazybones!

145
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:35,240
I've been so tired.

146
00:09:35,280 --> 00:09:36,740
I'll play with you in a bit.

147
00:09:37,680 --> 00:09:39,240
No, no!

148
00:09:39,280 --> 00:09:41,680
Get up and take me to Disneyland.

149
00:09:41,680 --> 00:09:43,840
We had a deal a long time ago!

150
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:44,760
How about this?

151
00:09:44,760 --> 00:09:47,080
Count my beard first.

152
00:09:47,280 --> 00:09:48,320
Once you're done,

153
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,080
I'll get up.

154
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:53,080
One, two, three, four,

155
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,720
five, six, seven,

156
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:55,760
eight, nine,

157
00:09:55,760 --> 00:09:56,720
ten...

158
00:09:59,640 --> 00:10:00,360
Xia,

159
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:03,040
I can't take you to Disneyland today.

160
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:06,360
But I promise you one last time.

161
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:08,800
I'll definitely take you there next week.

162
00:10:08,800 --> 00:10:10,400
-Pinky swear?
-Pinky swear.

163
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:13,240
Pinky swear,

164
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:15,480
forever and ever.

165
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:37,400
Go.

166
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,860
The plane ticket is under the box.

167
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:43,440
Go south.

168
00:10:44,440 --> 00:10:45,520
Never look back.

169
00:10:48,880 --> 00:10:49,740
What about you?

170
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,840
It doesn't matter where I am.

171
00:10:58,160 --> 00:10:59,720
I only want to see

172
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:03,920
a sunrise every morning
without the shadow of hatred.

173
00:11:13,800 --> 00:11:15,280
Lu Fan, look at you.

174
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:18,360
Our company is your home now, huh?

175
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:20,520
Listen, if we hadn't found you in time,

176
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:21,680
you would've died from overwork,

177
00:11:21,680 --> 00:11:22,440
okay?

178
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:25,920
Is he still like this every day?

179
00:11:25,920 --> 00:11:27,200
Drinking and working overtime every day

180
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:28,260
without sleeping?

181
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,980
Just keep torturing yourself

182
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,200
for Su Xia, okay?

183
00:11:40,920 --> 00:11:41,880
Get out!

184
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:45,520
Look at you now.

185
00:11:46,800 --> 00:11:48,330
We've got news about Su Xia.

186
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:50,370
Can you get revenge?

187
00:11:54,920 --> 00:11:56,250
Do you know where she is?

188
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:07,160
Mr. Lu,

189
00:12:07,560 --> 00:12:09,820
I'll definitely pay you back next month.

190
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:12,130
That vixen took the money and ran away!

191
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:13,000
I...

192
00:12:13,640 --> 00:12:15,640
I stood by you when you started over,

193
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:16,980
so please go easy on me!

194
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:22,320
You were deceived by a woman?

195
00:12:23,760 --> 00:12:25,760
I guess you deserve two broken legs.

196
00:12:27,160 --> 00:12:27,840
No, no!

197
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:28,720
Mr. Lu, I'm begging you!

198
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:29,760
I'm sorry!

199
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:30,800
Su Xia, Su Xia!

200
00:12:30,800 --> 00:12:31,800
I saw Su Xia!

201
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:38,370
What did you say?

202
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:40,160
Two days ago,

203
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:41,440
when I was inspecting the cemetery,

204
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,840
I saw her there.

205
00:12:42,840 --> 00:12:43,640
Xiao Qi was with her.

206
00:12:43,640 --> 00:12:44,900
It was definitely her!

207
00:12:46,560 --> 00:12:47,920
Do you know how you'll end up

208
00:12:47,920 --> 00:12:49,480
if you lie to me?

209
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:50,520
Oh, no,

210
00:12:50,520 --> 00:12:51,320
I wouldn't dare lie to you!

211
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:53,000
Every word I said is true!

212
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,730
I'm telling the truth, I swear!

213
00:13:01,280 --> 00:13:02,320
Confirm it.

214
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:03,800
Get out.

215
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:10,000
You too.

216
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:11,980
Thanks, Mr. Lu.

217
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:16,800
Three years,

218
00:13:18,160 --> 00:13:19,400
160 countries,

219
00:13:20,280 --> 00:13:21,840
637 cities.

220
00:13:22,520 --> 00:13:23,780
You finally showed up,

221
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:25,960
Su Xia,

222
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:29,120
you should've hidden yourself better.

223
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:30,770
Unfortunately,

224
00:13:31,480 --> 00:13:33,120
you have a fatal weakness.
